<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">6. Cruze as </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">i</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">nforma&ccedil;&otilde;es</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW239111931 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW239111931 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Cruzar informa&ccedil;&otilde;es de diferentes fontes &eacute; essencial para validar dados e obter uma vis&atilde;o mais completa. Essa etapa ajuda a evitar vieses e garante a precis&atilde;o dos resultados.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW239111931 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW239111931 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">7. Finalize com </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">e</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">xcel&ecirc;ncia</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW239111931 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW239111931 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>A &uacute;ltima etapa do Desk </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">Research</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"> &eacute; consolidar todas as informa&ccedil;&otilde;es coletadas e apresentar os insights de maneira clara e objetiva. Isso facilita a tomada de decis&otilde;es e o planejamento estrat&eacute;gico.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW239111931 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW239111931 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Exemplos Pr&aacute;ticos</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW239111931 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW239111931 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Exemplo 1: Pinterest </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">Predicts</span></span><span class="LineBreakBlob BlobObject DragDrop SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="SCXW239111931 BCX8">&nbsp;</span><br class="SCXW239111931 BCX8"></span><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Estudos focados em setores espec&iacute;ficos, como o Pinterest </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW239111931 BCX8">Predicts</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">, s&atilde;o uma boa estrat&eacute;gia para entender os movimentos macro de cada player do setor.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW239111931 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW239111931 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Exemplo 2: Embrapa</span></span><span class="LineBreakBlob BlobObject DragDrop SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="SCXW239111931 BCX8">&nbsp;</span><br class="SCXW239111931 BCX8"></span><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Empresas como a Embrapa frequentemente divulgam suas leituras sobre futuros movimentos de mercado, sendo fontes confi&aacute;veis para tend&ecirc;ncias no setor agro.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW239111931 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW239111931 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Exemplo 3: Inova&ccedil;&otilde;es </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">e</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">mergentes</span></span><span class="LineBreakBlob BlobObject DragDrop SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="SCXW239111931 BCX8">&nbsp;</span><br class="SCXW239111931 BCX8"></span><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Ao analisar novas tecnologias, &eacute; crucial observar se elas t&ecirc;m alinhamento com as propostas dos grandes players. A inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta, onde empresas se conectam com startups para trazer novas solu&ccedil;&otilde;es, est&aacute; se tornando uma pr&aacute;tica comum.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW239111931 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8">&nbsp;</p>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">Avan&ccedil;ando no Desk </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">Research</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">: Quatro Etapas Essenciais</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Na primeira parte deste artigo, discutimos tr&ecirc;s elementos cruciais para a constru&ccedil;&atilde;o de um bom Desk </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">Research</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8"> no contexto de projetos de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o. Agora, vamos explorar quatro quest&otilde;es igualmente importantes para que esse processo seja &aacute;gil e eficiente:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">1. Consulte Especialistas</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Conversar com especialistas do setor pode enriquecer significativamente o Desk </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">Research</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">. Entrevistas com profissionais experientes podem fornecer insights valiosos sobre suas viv&ecirc;ncias, vis&atilde;o de mercado e expectativas para o futuro. Idealmente, voc&ecirc; deve consultar um n&uacute;mero consider&aacute;vel de especialistas, que podem incluir acad&ecirc;micos, empres&aacute;rios, jornalistas e pessoas atualmente atuando no setor de interesse.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">2. Pausa para Reflex&atilde;o</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>At&eacute; este ponto, voc&ecirc; coletou muitas informa&ccedil;&otilde;es. No entanto, esses dados n&atilde;o ter&atilde;o muito valor se n&atilde;o forem analisados e compilados de maneira que permita a extra&ccedil;&atilde;o de resultados significativos. Esta etapa de consolida&ccedil;&atilde;o pode ocorrer ao final do Desk </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">Research</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8"> ou como uma fase intermedi&aacute;ria. Se, ap&oacute;s uma </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW244776898 BCX8">pr&eacute;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">-compila&ccedil;&atilde;o, os resultados ainda parecerem superficiais, pode ser necess&aacute;rio intensificar as buscas em algumas &aacute;reas.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">3. Cruzamento de Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Ap&oacute;s mergulhar no assunto e coletar insights de v&aacute;rias frentes e especialistas, voc&ecirc; ter&aacute; um grande volume de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es. Agora &eacute; hora de combinar esses elementos para gerar resultados. Dependendo do objetivo do projeto, voc&ecirc; pode extrair diferentes n&iacute;veis de consolida&ccedil;&atilde;o:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW244776898 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">Sinais</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">: Indica&ccedil;&otilde;es iniciais como uma startup disruptiva que recebeu investimento significativo, movimentos estrat&eacute;gicos de grandes players ou novas legisla&ccedil;&otilde;es que impactam o mercado.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW244776898 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">Tend&ecirc;ncias</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">: Baseadas nos sinais, as tend&ecirc;ncias exigem uma an&aacute;lise cr&iacute;tica para determinar seu impacto a curto, m&eacute;dio e longo prazo. &Eacute; importante identificar se a tend&ecirc;ncia &eacute; emergente ou consolidada, e que tipo de mudan&ccedil;a ela representa.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW244776898 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">Transforma&ccedil;&otilde;es</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">: Conjunto de tend&ecirc;ncias analisadas que apontam para grandes mudan&ccedil;as no mercado. Isso pode incluir movimentos ESG, consolida&ccedil;&atilde;o de modelos de neg&oacute;cios ou tecnologias emergentes com potencial significativo. A an&aacute;lise das transforma&ccedil;&otilde;es deve ser baseada em </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">fatos</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8"> e avalia&ccedil;&otilde;es de especialistas.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">4. S&iacute;ntese Final</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW244776898 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Com o Desk </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8">Research</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW244776898 BCX8"> conclu&iacute;do e as informa&ccedil;&otilde;es compiladas, &eacute; hora de considerar o cen&aacute;rio geral que essas informa&ccedil;&otilde;es revelam. Al&eacute;m das tend&ecirc;ncias e transforma&ccedil;&otilde;es, qual &eacute; a vis&atilde;o macro resultante de todo esse esfor&ccedil;o? &Agrave;s vezes, atingir o est&aacute;gio de tend&ecirc;ncias e transforma&ccedil;&otilde;es j&aacute; &eacute; suficiente para fornecer os insights necess&aacute;rios para o projeto. No entanto, se voc&ecirc; deseja ir mais longe, pode alinhar todo o material com um horizonte temporal e projetar um cen&aacute;rio futuro para o mercado-alvo do seu estudo. Esse cen&aacute;rio levar&aacute; em conta todas as transforma&ccedil;&otilde;es identificadas, oferecendo uma vis&atilde;o abrangente das inova&ccedil;&otilde;es, impactos no setor e novas perspectivas de consumo e produtos.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW244776898 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW239111931 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">Conclus&atilde;o</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW239111931 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW239111931 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>O Desk </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8">Research</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW239111931 BCX8"> &eacute; uma ferramenta poderosa para alinhar a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o com a estrat&eacute;gia empresarial. Com uma abordagem estruturada e estrat&eacute;gica, as empresas podem explorar novas oportunidades e se manter &agrave; frente no mercado em constante evolu&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW239111931 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW239111931 BCX8">&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Sobre a Avantt.i&nbsp;</h3>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>A Avantt.i &eacute; uma plataforma de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o desenvolvida pela Inventta, para gestores de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o e gerentes de projeto.</p>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Com m&oacute;dulos de intra, open e gest&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio, oferecemos uma vis&atilde;o completa da Gest&atilde;o da Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o para alavancar suas iniciativas.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Vis&atilde;o global e gest&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio: </strong>Atrav&eacute;s da consolida&ccedil;&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o, a Avantt.i ajuda a identificar os principais projetos e avan&ccedil;ar com assertividade. Tudo em uma &uacute;nica plataforma.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Programa de intra: </strong>Crie desafios e obtenha participa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos colaboradores. A inova&ccedil;&atilde;o vira rotina e voc&ecirc; impulsiona a cultura de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o na empresa.</li>
<li><strong>Open Innovation:</strong> Chame startups e parceiros para desafios, gerencie parceria na plataforma e tenha acesso a mais de 23.000 startups na nossa base.</li>
<li><strong>M&eacute;tricas Acion&aacute;veis: </strong>Influencie a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o a investir em esfor&ccedil;os de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o com base em m&eacute;tricas claras e acion&aacute;veis. Me&ccedil;a resultados dos projetos e comunique o sucesso das iniciativas</li>
<li><strong>Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o Integrada e Transparente: </strong>Gerencie projetos de diferentes esteiras e horizontes, com colabora&ccedil;&atilde;o de parceiros e equipe, visualizando o portf&oacute;lio globalmente.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>Engajamento com Conhecimento: </strong>Transforme a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o em h&aacute;bito com trilhas de conhecimento e mentorias dispon&iacute;veis ao longo da jornada.&nbsp;<br><br>Conhe&ccedil;a <a href="https://materiais.avanttinovacao.com.br/avantti-inovacao-primeiro-passo">aqui</a>, solicite uma demonstra&ccedil;&atilde;o guiada e teste gr&aacute;tis.<a href="https://materiais.avanttinovacao.com.br/avantti-inovacao-primeiro-passo"><span class="EOP SCXW195930854 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img src="https://d335luupugsy2.cloudfront.net/cms/files/808420/1720784635/$63vucuqtfj9" width="673" height="448"></span></a></li>
</ul>
